metadata.name: Dotak || Jeune de Auberge.i
metadata.description:
Dotak, meaning dots in the plural of Basque.

It is a curated series from Dotak, a hand-coded generative exploration of circles with carefully curated color palettes. Intentionally induced randomness on divisibility on the frame delivers very unique and insightful pieces. Scripted in p5js.

3600x3600px, PNG.

An original artwork by Jox, 2022.
